Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:09.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,When watching Hayate no Gotoku, make sure to watch at a good distance away from the TV in a well lit room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:09.95,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:27.87,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Screen Text: "While walking outside, harm befalls the local residences"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:41.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What movie is this, Milady?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:36.88,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Screen Text: Sada
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:43.29,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It is very avant-garde.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:48.58,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When I rented a video from Wataru,\Nthis looked interesting, so I borrowed it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:51.73,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently I'll die if I don't show it to two other people within one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:56.09,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What? Isn't that the same curse as that circular movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:01.87,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Such an unscientific thing can't possibly exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:05.92,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You have a childish side to you, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:08.20,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.93,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.93,0:01:13.56,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The circular movie is the famous Ri-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.81,0:01:14.95,Default-alt,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't say any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:18.46,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who serves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is one who dedicates himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:27.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A butler is a formal guardian who supports the days of their master.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.14,0:01:30.24,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.24,0:01:38.03,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is a super combat battle story of a boy who fights, risking his life for a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:41.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's the Obon festival now,\Nthe season for ghost stories, did I react too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.60,0:01:43.11,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's Obon, no one's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.11,0:01:44.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,From here on, we're working the cel artists into the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:23.17,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Nagi... She's past the return date again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:26.91,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that O****'s works\Nrequire more than one viewing to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:31.82,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that circular movie's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:34.93,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Someone actually rented that fake copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:41.80,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Saki, Nagi's overdue with the rental, so give her a call, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.11,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:56.08,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week since, but nothing has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.23,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's as I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.35,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Spirits do not exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:07.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:10.80,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She looks so mature;\NI bet she doesn't have anything she's bad at.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:14.34,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I just remembered we have watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.34,0:04:15.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to enjoy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.67,0:04:18.46,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's give it to Milady, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:22.77,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I already took some to Nagi, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.42,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, this won't cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.45,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there a more striking name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:33.08,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to find a new genre with horror imbedded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:39.52,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I see. When it comes to manga,\Nshe gets engrossed in it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.46,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Although that's what's good about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.08,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Give one to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru-kun, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:52.10,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Well you know, Nagi's been overdue with her rental again, so I'm here to bug her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.39,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Right, what was that strange movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:05:00.47,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed it was missing from the shelf, so it was Nagi who took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:04.12,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fake version made when the authentic one was popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.87,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think someone who would want to watch that crap existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.16,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Sa**ko doesn't even come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.55,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, something like this comes out when you watch that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:21.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if something like that existed, it would be gross, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:22.72,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.14,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.70,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Saki's been acting strangely recently. {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:39.65,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's worried about something, but won't talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:45.69,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, just because she's twenty now, does she want to say a thirteen year old isn't reliable enough for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:50.03,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Saki-san is going to\Nher Coming-of-Age Ceremony next year, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.49,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Coming-of-Age Ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.70,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you'll be twenty when June comes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:58.58,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.81,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I should get you something to celebrate, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:01.94,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:03.78,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,That kindness is enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:06.67,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,You always wear that maid outfit so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:09.05,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,What me to buy you a furisode?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.05,Note,Note,0000,0000,0000,,Furisode: An elegant kimono for unwed women.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.59,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean that, Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.32,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,When you become twenty, you'll need one for your Coming-of-Age Ceremony, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:19.36,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't need one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.52,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:25.33,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll look forward to it without too much expectation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:33.14,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be upset because I forgot about her birthday and didn't give her the furisode I promised her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.84,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are birthdays and Coming-of-Age Ceremonies important?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.73,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:42.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what was your Coming-of-Age Ceremony like, Maria-san? {ep 18}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:44.43,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.36,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:50.32,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Maira-san's only seventeen, so she hasn't had hers yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:54.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am still a fresh seventeen year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.59,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, Hayate-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.86,0:07:00.63,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,What made you think I have had my Coming-of-Age ceremony?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:04.34,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,M-Maria-san, you're acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:07.50,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:10.81,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I just remembered something I need to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:14.96,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Really, what's wrong with Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:17.73,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Coming-of-Age Ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.81,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll ask Saki personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.93,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:33.80,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Could the reason why you've been sighing be because I forgot about your birthday present?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:37.24,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, nobody celebrated my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.83,0:07:41.71,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind though, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:50.21,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything about the time that's passed, but I think the lost trust can be rebuilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:53.66,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you need from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.79,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I want to give you a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:55.35,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't need one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.73,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd ever give you a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:05.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,When you ask others for a favor,\N"watch what you say," says Haman****.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:05.86,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:12.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Really, it's better for her to play with\Nher friends than draw manga all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go make some tea for the two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:17.01,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So, what's this present thing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:23.45,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see, I want to give a furisode to a certain person,\Nbut I don't have a clue what's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:26.83,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, a furisode as a gift, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.83,0:08:28.72,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so you've finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.49,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Go to this store.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:35.19,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty cheap, and you can find variety of furisode your girl would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.39,0:08:36.94,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.39,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a bunch, Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.39,0:08:40.20,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:42.77,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,But don't buy something too cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:49.66,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask just in case, but how much does an average furisode cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.66,0:08:52.20,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's cheaper than buying two Fe***ris.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.20,0:08:55.41,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,How could clothes be more expensive than a Fe***ri?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.41,0:08:58.30,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of a commoner's sense of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:08:59.98,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Stop shouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:02.65,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The chair I hit you with cost more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.99,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of furniture do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if a man decides to give a present to a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:12.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,it's natural to pay that much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:13.11,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,You're worthless if you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:15.86,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You may have a point, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.57,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Where do I find such money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:23.24,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's not carved in stone, we are engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.82,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So no interest and pay me back when you make the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.65,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.57,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,So bright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:42.73,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Holy Onmyouji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.49,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here, Maria-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:46.81,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Something {\i1}is{\fscx50} {\r} wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.63,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,H-How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.63,0:09:50.44,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.33,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.57,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:04.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Nothing but that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:06.92,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot handle that black rustling creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.85,0:10:11.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Maria-san had this side to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:17.00,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry; I lost control of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.16,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,But I just cannot stand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:24.07,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it does appear, I will protect you, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.04,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really? You really will?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:42.25,Default,Roach,0000,0000,0000,,Roach...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.03,0:10:45.76,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:48.33,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:51.04,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate-kun... What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.69,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry, Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:10:58.10,Default,Roach,0000,0000,0000,,Roach!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.16,0:11:02.18,Default,Roach,0000,0000,0000,,Roach?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.18,0:11:03.94,Default,Roach,0000,0000,0000,,Cock Roach Roach Roach Roach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.64,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Ima aini yukimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.49,0:11:08.64,Note,2,0000,0000,0000,,Ima aini yukimasu. = We'll come see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.95,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Su... Suusuu surun desu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.34,0:11:13.95,Note,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Su... Suusuu surun desu. = I... I feel a chill down my spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:22.05,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know Sir was worried about my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:26.60,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to that, Grandma won't even call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.04,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to explain for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:33.16,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Kijima Saki's grandmother is the legendary housemaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:35.18,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Kijima Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:37.76,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In order to find her missing daughter and son-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.76,0:11:39.82,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Saki's parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:43.35,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,at times, she wandered around the world with Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:47.55,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,At times, she protected the president from assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:54.19,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,At times, she closed cases that would have been filed away forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:03.68,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And at times, she liberated oppressed citizens by serving delicious cuisine to emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:08.17,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, the legendary maid is already sixty-two years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:11.86,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her life was about to end in the middle of the Sahara Desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.02,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:17.30,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan to die here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:19.98,Default,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the legendary housemaid, Kijima Rei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.54,0:12:25.76,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This man is the President of\Nthe Tachibana Group, Tachibana Enkyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:31.13,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Kijima Rei and Saki were saved by Enkyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:35.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,A resonance between hearts that's neither friendship nor love blooms between Enkyou and Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:40.00,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,In order to repay the debt, Rei fights against evil and criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.37,0:12:43.84,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And, a fated encounter came to Saki, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.08,0:12:47.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Her encounter with Wataru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:52.12,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,His too-young-to-be-a-mother mother didn't give much attention to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.02,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Saki swore to his lonely face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.02,0:13:00.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...that she shall repay the gratitude of saving\NKijima Rei back by raising him to be a wonderful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.00,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.65,0:13:10.78,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,To Saki, it felt like two souls forsaken by mothers were calling to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.54,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I serve tea better than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:20.98,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But Wataru was very skilled and could do everything himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:24.94,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was so much more thorough than Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:31.92,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Could I possibly guide him to become a wonderful man?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:35.71,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,For your reference, Saki's parents still live in Ueno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.00,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They are not lost, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:52.57,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.71,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Please hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:01.99,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:07.23,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:13.47,Default,Kla,0000,0000,0000,,On days like this, it's best to walk around creating the original language of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:18.87,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Target spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:22.62,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Jet St***m Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:25.68,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.78,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:30.45,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:39.87,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:41.78,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Another round of Jet St***m Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.36,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:48.37,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Jet St***m!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.40,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:56.71,Default,Robo,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you step on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:01.27,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We should be fine, since we've come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On what basis?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.60,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:09.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,That was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:11.89,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,No, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.37,0:15:16.94,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you're persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.56,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:21.84,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:42.32,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I will not forgive you if you touch Hayate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.92,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:02.13,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.03,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.01,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:09.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I talked big saying I'd protect you, but I got protected instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.84,0:16:11.93,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:14.12,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,You did protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:15.86,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Maria-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.56,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, what if that thing attacks Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.43,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Milady's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:33.71,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised I did not get lost for once, but it seems as though we have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:50.15,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi-san, you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:54.33,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see the black rustling creature here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.56,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,That child already left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:01.37,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,She exterminated it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:03.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ruckus here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.00,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.84,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.81,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Did Wataru give you a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:11.83,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:14.28,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,He must be embarrassed inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:25.20,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,When you buy a present, you have to use your own money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:29.36,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,When I bought something with my savings, I could afford only a yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.16,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a cute yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.11,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.54,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. But why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:46.45,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi said there's something important you need to tell me and that you had a present waiting,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I should go to your house right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.03,0:17:52.02,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Could the present be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.77,0:17:53.81,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,...that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.55,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.82,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's the important thing you need to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:01.89,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,That Nagi, doing the extra unneeded favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.16,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,But this is an unexpected opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:08.47,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give this yukata to Isumi and tell her my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.50,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:15.97,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:17.34,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:21.78,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,I got ahold of an extra DVD box of Cha***ion, so I'll give you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.23,0:18:23.23,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:25.52,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,So what's the important thing you need to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:28.35,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the acting by Hagino-san, the main character.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:31.22,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike Ryu** Asakura, his acting is cheerful and worth a watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.41,0:18:34.48,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good watch when you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.43,Default,Isu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, thank you, Wataru-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.28,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:52.61,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:18:54.98,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.82,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.31,0:19:04.11,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I felt bad for forgetting about it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:08.83,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I can smell the scent of a female that's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:09.59,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:14.91,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't possibly bring a girl in while I was away and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.41,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,...do anything naughty...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:19.00,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.97,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,It's a present for you! This yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:24.84,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:30.12,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I didn't have enough money, I couldn't buy a furisode,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:35.17,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,and I had forgotten to get you a present for your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:38.56,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought that's why you were down recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:45.70,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what color I should get for my new cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:47.03,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.11,Default,Wat,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.83,0:20:11.14,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. It wasn't a present for Isumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:12.82,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.82,0:20:15.25,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,And did you lend him the money, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:21.37,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,No, he said it's pointless unless he buys it with his own money, so he bought a cheaper yukata instead of a furisode.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:22.55,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,One that's about fifty thousand yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.60,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty thousand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:24.94,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,That's not cheap at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.97,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, that circular creature didn't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:31.11,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's all made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:33.68,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:34.93,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:36.94,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.94,0:20:39.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Did a missile come flying from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.02,0:20:42.04,Default,Mar,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fireworks show nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:43.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:45.23,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Can't miss these in summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:47.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go out, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.57,0:20:49.16,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.60,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,The grilled squid is the best thing in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.03,0:21:14.22,Default,Wak,0000,0000,0000,,You look great in that yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:17.62,Default,Saki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:22.43,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe a new misunderstanding has arisen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.81,0:21:26.16,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.02,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's beautiful, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:35.83,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:42.75,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Roach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:52.91,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next week, the dragon and the hamster go head-to-head for their loved one with their pride at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.48,0:23:31.41,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.41,0:23:32.47,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.27,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Network!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.27,0:23:36.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Red Cross Killer, Sanzein Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.30,0:23:37.06,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ayasaki Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.28,0:23:39.33,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,It's really getting hot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.33,0:23:41.30,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Today's temperature at noon was over 30 degrees Celsius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:43.31,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't make things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.40,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know if the broadcast date will be really hot or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.51,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,The broadcast date differs depending on area, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.37,0:23:53.84,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than that, what I want to say is\Non a hot day like this, the best thing to do is sit...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:56.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,...in a chilled room playing MMOs while listening to my character song.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:58.25,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,You can't spend such an unhealthy summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.49,0:23:59.92,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:02.64,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,All right, summer vacation starts today!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:07.13,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play MMOs and watch anime and draw manga and fool around to my heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.13,0:24:10.48,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I think you do those even on school days.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:14.42,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Even though the summer break's started,\NI don't feel cheerful at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.42,0:24:16.93,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what Hayate-kun's doing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.42,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Hayate no Gotoku.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.42,0:24:20.89,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,I Like Books, but Sing It, Great Submarine Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:23.52,Default,Nag,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the burglar hamster from sometime ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.52,0:24:25.94,Default,Nis,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a burglar hamster?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:28.45,Default,Hay,0000,0000,0000,,The sign of the guardian guides me.
